gwaComparison.description: Independent samples t-test comparing GWA between Regular and Irregular students

studyHoursVsGWA.description: Pearson correlation between study hours per day and GWA
studyHoursVsGWA.interpretation: Significant moderate negative correlation (more hours = better grades since lower GWA is better)

note: In the Philippine GWA system, lower values indicate better performance (1.0 = highest, 5.0 = failing)
